== 学术背景 ==
'''尼可籁·霍奇艾诺夫'''的音乐天赋很早就被发掘，五岁开始学习弹奏钢琴，随后前往[[莫斯科音乐学院|莫斯科音乐学院]]附属中央音乐学校就读。<ref name="Cavalletti Artists Management">{{Cite web|url=http://www.cavartists.com/en/pianists/nikolay-khozyainov|title=Nikolay Khozyainov|website=Cavalletti Artists Management}}</ref>  7岁时，他在莫斯科音乐学院大音乐厅（the Great Hall）首演，演奏韩德尔钢琴协奏曲。<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|url=http://europe.yamaha.com/en/artists/pianos_keyboards_instruments/nikolay_khozyainov/|title=Nikolay Khozyainov|date=July 2015|last=|first=|publisher=|website=Yamaha|access-date=July 2015}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=NikolayKhozyainov|title=Nikolay Khozyainov Handel Piano Concerto F-major Moscow, February 2000|date=2016-05-27|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HO84GV3lplw|accessdate=2016-05-31|archive-date=2021-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210718063742/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HO84GV3lplw}}</ref> 2010年， 他继续在莫斯科柴可夫斯基音乐学院求学并顺利完成学业。<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|url=http://europe.yamaha.com/en/artists/pianos_keyboards_instruments/nikolay_khozyainov/|title=Nikolay Khozyainov|date=July 2015|last=|first=|publisher=|website=Yamaha|access-date=July 2015}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theaterjones.com/ntx/2013vancliburninternationalpianocompetition/20130519072048/2013-05-19/Meet-the-Pianists-Nikolay-Khozyainov|title=Meet the Pianists: Nikolay Khozyainov|accessdate=4 April 2016|last1=Farrington|first1=Jones|website=Theater Jones|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805134726/http://www.theaterjones.com/ntx/2013vancliburninternationalpianocompetition/20130519072048/2013-05-19/Meet-the-Pianists-Nikolay-Khozyainov}}</ref> 目前他投入Arie Vardi教授的门下，在德国汉诺威音楽学院（Musikhochschule Hannover）研究所深造。 <ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nikolaykhozyainov.com/#!biography/c1enr|title=Nikolay Khozyainov Biography|date=|last=|first=|publisher=|website=Nikolay Khozyainov Official Website|access-date=}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://jp.yamaha.com/sp/products/musical-instruments/keyboards/pianist-lounge/hope/012/|title=Yamaha Pianist Lounge|date=August 2014|last=Kosaka|first=Haruka|publisher=|website=Yamaha|access-date=}}</ref>

== 演出 ==
尼可籁·霍奇艾诺夫的重要演出包括在如下音乐厅举办钢琴独奏或协奏会： 卡内基音乐厅、<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.carnegiehall.org/Calendar/2013/4/30/0730/PM/Nikolay-Khozyainov-Piano/|title=Nikolay Khozyainov, Piano|website=www.carnegiehall.org|access-date=2016-05-31|archive-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624091926/http://www.carnegiehall.org/Calendar/2013/4/30/0730/PM/Nikolay-Khozyainov-Piano/}}</ref>伦敦威格莫尔大厅、<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.russianmind.eu/content/nikolay-khozyainov-make-wigmore-hall-debut-may-2014|title=Nikolay Khozyainov to make Wigmore Hall debut in May 2014|date=2014-03-11|website=www.russianmind.eu|access-date=2016-05-31|archive-date=2019-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301074442/http://www.russianmind.eu/content/nikolay-khozyainov-make-wigmore-hall-debut-may-2014}}</ref> 华府林肯艺术中心和肯尼迪中心、巴黎香榭丽舍剧院、加沃音乐厅（Salle Gaveau）、<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ladepeche.fr/article/2015/07/24/2148952-musee-du-piano-l-etonnant-pianiste-nikolay-khozyainov.html|title=Musée du Piano : l'étonnant pianiste Nikolay Khozyainov|website=ladepeche.fr|access-date=2016-05-31}}</ref> 莫斯科柴可夫斯基音乐厅、<ref name=":9">{{Cite web|url=http://www.meloman.ru/concert/05032015/?|title=Госоркестр России имени Е.Ф.Светланова, Елена Таросян, Анастасия Кобекина, Николай Хозяинов|website=www.meloman.ru|access-date=2016-05-31|archive-date=2021-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210625080754/https://meloman.ru/concert/05032015/}}</ref> 东京三得利音乐厅（Suntory Hall）和<ref name=":10">{{Cite web|url=http://www.suntory.com/culture-sports/suntoryhall/schedule/detail/20150419_M_2.html|title=TOKYO SYMPHONY ORCHESTRA SUBSCRIPTION CONCERT NO.629 Performance Schedule SUNTORY HALL|website=www.suntory.com|access-date=2016-05-31|archive-date=2019-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301074711/https://www.suntory.com/culture-sports/suntoryhall/schedule/detail/20150419_M_2.html}}</ref>罗浮宫等。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.louvre.fr/nikolay-khozyainov-piano|title=Nikolay{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} Khozyainov, piano {{!}} Musée du Louvre {{!}} Paris|website=www.louvre.fr|access-date=2016-05-31|archive-date=2019-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301141548/https://www.louvre.fr/nikolay-khozyainov-piano}}</ref>

